inline int scan(){
    char c = getchar_unlocked();
    int x = 0;
    while(c<'0'||c>'9'){

    }
    while(c>='0'&&c<='9'){
        x=(x<<1)+(x<<3)+c-'0';
        c=getchar_unlocked();
    }
    return x;
}
